snippet.title: Private Eye teaser - OculusVR thriller game
snippet.description:
The teaser trailer to the upcoming psychological, thriller built from the ground up for the Oculus Rift, Private Eye.  The game was originally developed as part of the Oculus Rift VR Jam competition and made it to the final.  The new edition aims to bring a heavily atmospheric and cinematic experience to the rift, mixing voyeurism and mystery in a 1950s New York environment.

Please support our Kickstarter that will launch alongside a demo.  Visit the official site for more info - http://www.privateeyevr.com
